 The white man can dance to African music wrote Gerhard Botha in a caption in SeSotho above the video clip which has been viewed nearly 600,000 times in just over a week.The video starts with him puffing on a cigarette barefoot wearing shorts next to a bakkie.Then the beat drops and his hips start moving. People can be heard in the background egging him and he drops to the floor showing off his stellar dance moves. OMG I am crying posted Britney Holland.Charlie Graham chipped in with This guy is just the best. Such a groover. Yemurai Mapurisa added True African dancing. What do you think?